# Xcode
*.xcuserdata
*.xcscmblueprint
xcuserdata/
DerivedData/
build/

# Secrets — Secrets.xcconfig is intentionally committed because the values
# inside it (legacy Supabase anon JWT + pk Mapbox public token + project URL)
# all ship in the client IPA anyway and are designed to be public. The only
# truly-secret value (MAPBOX_DOWNLOADS_TOKEN, sk.…) lives in ~/.netrc locally
# and as a Shared env var on Xcode Cloud — not in this file. Rotate the
# committed values via the Supabase + Mapbox dashboards before launch.

